snippet.title: BEYOND: TWO SOULS OFFICIAL PC TRAILER [EN]
snippet.description:
Buy now: https://www.epicgames.com/store/product/beyond-two-souls/home

Beyond: Two Souls, the critically-lauded interactive drama from Quantic Dream starring Ellen Page and Willem Dafoe is coming July 22 to PC exclusively on the Epic Games Store.

Subscribe to our newsletter: https://bit.ly/2UW2hTr
